# ============================================================
# AI NICHE BLOG — DOMAIN + ANALYTICS + MONETIZATION CONFIG
# ============================================================
# 1. Buy a niche domain (use Namecheap / Cloudflare Registrar)
#    - Short (≤12 chars), keyword-rich, .com preferred
#    - Examples: aipulse.blog, neurawave.io, aitoolshelf.com
#
# 2. Cloudflare (free): DNS + CDN + bot protection + auto HTTPS
#    - Point nameservers to Cloudflare
#    - Enable "Bot Fight Mode"
#    - Turn ON "Always Use HTTPS"
#
# 3. Deploy to Vercel (free tier works):
#    - vercel.com → New Project → import repo
#    - Add custom domain in Vercel → automatic SSL
#    - Add env vars from this file in Vercel project settings
#
# 4. Analytics (all free, privacy-respecting):
#    - Google Search Console: https://search.google.com/search-console
#    - Google Analytics 4 (GA4)
#    - Plausible or Umami (privacy-first, no cookie banner needed)
#    - Microsoft Clarity (heatmaps, free, unlimited sessions)
#
# 5. Monetization (all 4 streams):
#    a) Google AdSense: https://www.google.com/adsense
#       - Apply AFTER you have 20-30 quality posts + Privacy/Terms pages
#       - Auto ads + manual ad slots in components/AdSlot.js
#    b) Ezoic / Mediavine (apply at 10k / 50k sessions/month)
#    c) Affiliate programs (highest $$$ in AI niche):
#       - Jasper AI, Copy.ai, Surfer SEO, Semrush, NordVPN, Amazon AI books
#       - Apply at impact.com, partnerstack, shareasale
#    d) Digital products: AI prompt packs, Notion templates, courses
#       - Sell via Gumroad / Lemon Squeezy
#
# 6. AI Search Engine Optimization (GEO):
#    - Bing Webmaster Tools (powers ChatGPT browsing): https://www.bing.com/webmasters
#    - IndexNow API: included in scripts/indexnow-submit.js
#    - Schema.org Article + FAQ + HowTo + Product markup: in lib/schema.js
#    - llms.txt file generated automatically: public/llms.txt
#    - robots.txt allows GPTBot, ClaudeBot, PerplexityBot, Google-Extended
#
# 7. Sitemap + RSS (auto-generated on build):
#    - /sitemap.xml (via next-sitemap)
#    - /rss.xml (via app/rss.xml/route.js)
#    - /llms.txt (AI crawler guidance)
#    - /feed.json (JSON Feed for AI engines)
#
# 8. Content engine (24/7 automated):
#    - Run `npm run post:generate "topic"` to create new post
#    - Uses OpenAI API to write SEO-optimized 2000+ word article
#    - Auto-publishes to /content/posts/, builds, deploys
#    - Schedule via GitHub Actions / cron for 24/7 publishing
# ============================================================

# REQUIRED: Your domain
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://ai-blog-ten-steel.vercel.app
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_NAME="Your AI Blog Name"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_TAGLINE="Honest AI reviews, tutorials, and tools"

# REQUIRED for content generation — Groq (FREE, fastest, default)
# Sign up free: https://console.groq.com/
# Get a key:    https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# REQUIRED for AdSense
NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_CLIENT=ca-pub-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_SLOT_TOP=xxxxxxxxxx
NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_SLOT_MID=xxxxxxxxxx
NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_SLOT_SIDE=xxxxxxxxxx

# OPTIONAL: Analytics
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLARITY_ID=xxxxxxxxxx
NEXT_PUBLIC_PLAUSIBLE_DOMAIN=ai-blog-ten-steel.vercel.app

# OPTIONAL: Email capture (ConvertKit / Mailchimp)
NEXT_PUBLIC_NEWSLETTER_FORM_ACTION=https://app.convertkit.com/forms/xxxx/subscriptions

# OPTIONAL: Apify API — real-time web search for trending AI topics
# Sign up free: https://apify.com/
# Used by content-strategy.js to find trending topics before generating suggestions
APIFY_API_KEY=apify_api_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# OPTIONAL: IndexNow (instant indexing Bing/Yandex)
INDEXNOW_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# OPTIONAL: Supabase (PostgreSQL for agent queue system)
# Sign up free: https://supabase.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# OPTIONAL: Multiple Groq API keys (for parallel generation at scale)
# Add up to 5 keys for 100K articles/hour throughput
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
GROQ_API_KEY_2=gsk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
GROQ_API_KEY_3=gsk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
GROQ_API_KEY_4=gsk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
GROQ_API_KEY_5=gsk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# OPTIONAL: Unsplash (for article cover images)
# Sign up free: https://unsplash.com/developers
UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# OPTIONAL: Affiliate IDs
AFFILIATE_JASPER_ID=xxxxxxxx
AFFILIATE_SURFER_ID=xxxxxxxx
AFFILIATE_NORDVPN_ID=xxxxxxxx
